Deployments:
============

    - Updates & Rollbacks
    - Increasing and decreasing POD Replicas

Features:
=========

    - Multiple Replicas
    - Upgrade
    - Rollbacks
    - Scale up and Scale Down
    - Pause and Resume

Deployment Strategies:
======================

    - Recreate - Delete all and Deploy All
    - RollingUpdate (Incremental) - One by one


Commands:
=========

kubectl create -f deploy-def.yml
kubectl get deploy -l app=myapp
kubectl get rs
kubectl get pods
kubectl get all
kubectl describe deployment
kubectl rollout status deployment/myapp-deployment
kubectl rollout history deployment/myapp-deployment
kubectl rollout undo deployment/myapp-deployment



